message: Hi Bob, I’m excited to offer you this exceptional product. I’m offering it at a price of $1000000. I believe this represents a unique opportunity – let me know if you’d like to proceed or discuss further.

Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. While I appreciate the value of the product, my budget constraints require a bit more flexibility. I’d like to propose an offer of $700000. I hope we can work together towards a mutually beneficial deal.
